SUMMARY:713v3 Virtua Fighter 5 & Tekken 8 Tournament
DTSTAMP:20260620T023014Z
DTSTART:20260703T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:713v3 Houston’s 3v3 Tournament \nVIRTUA FIGHTER 5 & TEKKEN 8\nE
	very First Friday of the Month\n5 – 6:30 PM Casuals \n7 PM – Tournament St
